name: RS Medium - Non-Nutrient Medium (NNM) Component
description: The RS medium is a fully defined medium designed for growing diverse marine protists. RS medium presents a natural buffer system with a pH of ~7 and a salinity of 3,3%. It includes two components: the Non-Nutrient Medium (NNM) and the Nutrient Medium (NM). Here we show the preparation of the NNM.

name: RS Medium - Nutrient Medium (NM) Component
description: The RS medium is a fully defined medium designed for growing diverse marine protists. RS medium presents a natural buffer system with a pH of ~7 and a salinity of 3,3%. It includes two components: the Non-Nutrient Medium (NNM) and the Nutrient Medium (NM). Here we show the preparation of the NM.
